Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about Python. What is it, how does it work, and how you can get started today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All of that and more in two minutes. Start the timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.26,0:00:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Python is a prevalent general purpose programming language often used for machine learning and data analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Python was created by Guido van Rossum and was first released on February 20th, 1991.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This language is so influential that in 1999 the Zen of Python was released,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a guiding set of principles for using Python in the utmost Mr. Miyagi way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.10,0:00:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There are numerous reasons why this language is hotter than the Backstreet Boys were in 1997.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.74,0:00:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The first being that Python is very readable, like it states in the Zen of Python.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.68,0:00:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Simple is better than complex, and that's exactly what the language mirrors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Python can also handle a multitude of different jobs, from machine learning,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.14,0:00:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to data analytics, web development, testing, and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.46,0:00:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no need to debate how great this language is. But how can we use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.14,0:00:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can download Python on the official Getting Started With Python page.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.56,0:01:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Once downloaded, creating a file with Python is as easy as naming the file and ending it with .py.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.94,0:01:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,These files are also referred to as modules.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.26,0:01:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then all you need to do is print hello world and there you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You can brag to all your friends that you are the next Bill Gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.96,0:01:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You have probably heard of interpreted versus compiled, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.32,0:01:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Python is an interpreted language, which means the source code is converted into
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,byte code that is then executed by the Python virtual machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This equates to Python being extremely fast to develop, but not so fast during the execution
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,step since the code is not directly compiled and executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But why should we learn Python?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.94,0:01:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably the most important answer to that is just how beginner-friendly the language is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're brand new to web development, my recommendation is either learn Python or JavaScript.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.90,0:01:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't go wrong with either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,As we mentioned before, Python is also extremely versatile.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do so many different tasks with just one language.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Lastly, Python developers are extremely in demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.14,0:02:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 36,000 job postings on Zippercrooter at this current moment for entry-level Python
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,developers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.34,0:02:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to learn Python and fully master one of the most relevant languages
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world of development, check out Zero2Mastery's complete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.72,0:02:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Python Developer Bootcamp course, where you'll go from beginner to expert.

